18
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,240
I thought the divorce happened ages ago.

19
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:35,160
Him? When we were together,
he never treated me right.

20
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:37,720
Now that I want to end it,
he's refusing to let go.

21
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,640
Forget him. He's bad luck.

22
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,720
- Do you need a hand?
- No, no, don't.

23
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,960
- Careful.
- You're gonna break my arm--

24
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,600
- No, don't.
- Sorry, sorry, my bad.

25
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,440
- My arm…
- Sorry!

26
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:53,040
